window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Book One</p> <p>Hollowed Hills—A serial killer targeting young women, thrusts fear and chaos into the live of the residents of the small town of Hollowed Hills, Massachusetts. True Crime podcaster, Lorelei O'Donnell, obsessed with all things spooky, scary, and shocking, forces her way into the middle of the search for the murderer lurking in the shadows. After three bodies are discovered along the city's border, Lorelei hopes her investigative skills and avid online following can assist in ending this reign of terror. When Lorelei gets too close to the answers that weren't meant to be found, her game of cat and mouse turns on her. Now she is the prey.</p> <p>Book Two</p> <p>Haunted Hollow—Lorelei O'Donnell, a true-crime podcast host, has officially ended her search for the Hollowed Hills Killer. The case is closed, and the mystery has been solved. While the local police and residents of Hollowed Hills may not like the outcome of the hunt for their mysterious killer, Lorelei is ready to move on with her life. Her new relationship has become more than she ever hoped for. Murder and More with Lore is gaining dozens of new followers every day. She is preparing for this exciting new chapter in her life. She should be overjoyed, right? However, even now, months later, Lorelei is still on high alert, constantly looking over her shoulder and searching her surroundings for someone lurking in the shadows. The all-too-familiar feeling of being watched is more present now than ever.</p>"; 
